Odaily Planet Daily News Four.Meme platform's first pre-sale project SkyAI posted on the X platform that as an open source MCP technology community, it is committed to returning all profits to our supporters and participants. The SKYAI community will not retain any tokens or BNB. Pre-sale details are as follows: 
1. 80% of the tokens will be allocated through public pre-sales; 
2. 20% of the tokens will be used to increase liquidity; 
3. The hard cap of the pre-sale is 500 BNB, all of which will be used for liquidity; 
4. Any excess BNB will be refunded; 
5. 80% of the public pre-sale tokens will be fairly distributed according to the contribution ratio. 
Note: Transfers made directly from exchanges will also be counted. 
According to on-chain data, SkyAI finally raised 83,851 BNB, worth approximately US$49.31 million, 167 times more than the original amount.
